Class ImmutableRobotPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • ftc.team6460.javadeck.api.planner.ImmutableRobotPosition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RobotPosition

    public class ImmutableRobotPosition
extends java.lang.Object
implements RobotPosition
    Describes a robot position, that should not change. This may be used for things such as goal locations or logs of old data.
    See Also:
    The package-level javadoc describing coordinate systems and conventions.
